Updated : 11-Dec-2017  Application features:
- built-in player;
- favorites and playlists manager;
- support for playlists ".m3u", ".m3u8", ".asx", ".pls", ".xspf";
- availability of TV programs;
- ability to cast to the devices: Chromecast, Amazon Fire TV, Apple TV, Roku, WDTV, Smart
TVs, Other DLNA Renderers.
- simple and intuitive interface.

Unlike the free version:
- No advertisements;
- Advanced settings;
- Reconnection function.
